print(msg.upper())
print(msg.lower())
print(msg.capitalize())
msg='welcome to Python: Strings'
print(msg)
print(len(msg))
print(msg.count('o'))
print(msg.title())

output:
welcome to it's Python: Strings
WELCOME TO IT'S PYTHON: STRINGS
welcome to it's python: strings
Welcome to it's python: strings
welcome to Python: Strings
26
3
Welcome To Python: Strings


